1. Ona *planira* da otputuje za Beograd sutra. (She plans to travel to Belgrade tomorrow.)
2. Da li si *planirao* svoj budžet za ovaj mesec? (Have you planned your budget for this month?)
3. Mi *planiramo* da se vratimo kući do večeri. (We plan to return home by evening.)
4. Njihov tim *planira* da izgradi novu fabriku u gradu. (Their team plans to build a new factory in the city.)
5. On *planira* da kupi novi automobil ovog leta. (He plans to buy a new car this summer.)
6. Kako *planirate* da organizujete svoj godišnji odmor? (How do you plan to organize your annual vacation?)
7. Nakon sastanka, menadžer će *planirati* dalje korake za projekat. (After the meeting, the manager will plan the next steps for the project.)
8. Da li ćeš *planirati* da posetiš svoju porodicu tokom praznika? (Will you plan to visit your family during the holidays?)
9. Kompanija *planira* da poveća broj zaposlenih u narednoj godini. (The company plans to increase the number of employees next year.)
10. Ukoliko *nešto planiraš*, javi mi unapred da bih se pripremila. (If you plan something, let me know in advance so that I can prepare.)